data.meta_description: MEDINFAR  is a fully integrated Pharmaceutical company with headquarters in Lisbon, Portugal.
data.text: MEDINFAR is a fully integrated Pharmaceutical company with headquarters in Lisbon, Portugal. Medinfar outlicense a wide range of products: Rx medicines, Consumer Health, Dermacosmetics, Food Supplements and Veterinary products in more than 70 countries.
